{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-44","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">disrupt</span> znači intervenisati ili sprečiti da se nešto desi na normalan način. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Loud noises disrupt my concentration.</span> — Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">disrupt</span> znači da ti zvukovi remete ili odvlače pažnju nekoga.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">sleep cycle</span> To je prirodan obrazac koji prati telo tokom spavanja, prolazeći kroz različite faze kao što su lagani san i duboki san. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A good sleep cycle is vital for restful sleep.</span> — Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sleep cycle</span> znači dobar obrazac spavanja koji pomaže telu i umu da se adekvatno odmore.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-44"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta stručnjak misli kada kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">hitting the snooze button disrupts your sleep cycle</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Produžava ciklus spavanja.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Disrupts</span> ukazuje na intervenciju, nije potrebno povećavati trajanje ciklusa spavanja.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Narušava prirodnu strukturu vašeg spavanja.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Poboljšava kvalitet spavanja.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Disrupts</span> pokazuje negativan efekat, a ne poboljšava kvalitet spavanja.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Nema nikakvih uticaja na spavanje.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Disrupts</span> to znači da nešto uzrokuje problem ili narušava ciklus spavanja.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room1.png","characters":[{"character":"Expert","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"2.2-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":8.98,"finishTimestamp":19.58},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Expert","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Expert","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":6.42,"dialogue":{"text":"Absolutely. My first suggestion is to not hit the snooze button multiple times.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Expert","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.08,"finishTime":11.6,"dialogue":{"text":"It may be tempting, but it disrupts your sleep cycle and you may feel groggy during the day.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Expert","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":12.1,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 44","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","dashedName":"task-44","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-45","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-en